Abstract = {{Bees provide essential pollination services that are potentially
   affected both by local farm management and the surrounding landscape. To
   better understand these different factors, we modelled the relative
   effects of landscape composition (nesting and floral resources within
   foraging distances), landscape configuration (patch shape, interpatch
   connectivity and habitat aggregation) and farm management (organic vs.
