   spp.), pea (Pisium sativum L.), chickpeas (Cicer arietium L.), peanut
   (Arachis hypogaea L.), licorice (Giycyrrhiza glabra L.), sunflower
   (Helianthus annuus L.), and Canthamus tinctorius L. Furthermore, X.
   pubescens has a potential in using pollination of certain plants in
