   in the mangrove community of Setiu Wetlands. A total of 35 types of
   pollens were collected from the body of X. varipuncta and only 10 types
   of the pollens were successfully identified. The identified pollens were
   of Avicennia alba, Lumnitzera racemosa, Sonneratia caseolaris, S. ovata
   and Rhizophora apiculata from exclusive mangroves, while Suregada
   multiflora, Melaleuca cajuputi, Derris trifoliata, Acacia auriculiformis
